Package org.gvsig.mapsheets.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GridPropertiesPage  
    MapSheetSelectionDialog
    This dialog lets user choose a grid and choose active fields from which a new layout template will be created.
    MapSheetsSettingsPanel
    Dialog to create a new map sheet grid, by choosing creation method, overlapping, etc.
    MapSheetViewGridDialog
    Dialog to associate a new grid to a layout template.
    PrintSelectionDialog
    Dialog to browse map sheets (layout template will refresh) and print them with various options.
    PrintTaskWindow
    Print progress dialog used when printing to PDF files.
